creating IMAGE
Step 1:
cloneing git repo my-node-app
git clone https://github.com/KarthickSuresh09/my-node-app.git

Step 2:
creating the docker file "vi Dockerfile"
inside the docker file 
FROM node:13-alpine
WORKDIR /usr/app
COPY package*.json /usr/app
COPY app/* /usr/app
RUN npm install
CMD ["node", "server.js"]
